00:26:49,000 --> 00:26:53,000
 It was almost $2 billion to create,

441
00:26:53,000 --> 00:26:55,000
 and it basically was the telescope that went up into space.

442
00:26:55,000 --> 00:26:57,000
 I think we have a picture of it.

443
00:26:57,000 --> 00:26:59,000
 That allowed us to take images from space.

444
00:26:59,000 --> 00:27:00,000
 I mean, it was amazing.

445
00:27:00,000 --> 00:27:03,000
 It's incredible that NASA produced and sent off into space,

446
00:27:03,000 --> 00:27:06,000
 and it would allow us to see far distances into the universe

447
00:27:06,000 --> 00:27:10,000
 and also allow us to capture accurate footage of our world

448
00:27:10,000 --> 00:27:11,000
 and to see it more clearly.

